#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sale App</font></strong>"
" manages in-store orders and payments."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບ Point of Sale</font></strong> ຈັດກາ"
"ນຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ ແລະ ການຊຳລະເງິນຢູ່ໜ້າຮ້ານ."

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase App</font></strong> "
"manages raw material orders and vendors."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການຈັດຊື້</font></strong> ຈັດການຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ວັດ"
"ຖຸດິບ ແລະ ຜູ້ສະໜອງ."

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Sales App</font></strong> "
"streamlines customer orders and quotations, such as managing custom cake "
"requests."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການຂາຍ</font></strong> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ ແ"
"ລະ ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາມີຄວາມຄ່ອງຕົວ, ເຊັ່ນ: ການຈັດການຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍເຄັກຕາມສັ່ງ."

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Website &amp; eCommerce "
"App</font></strong> enables online sales."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບເວັບໄຊ ແລະ eCommerce</font></"
"strong> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ສາມາດຂາຍຜ່ານທາງອອນລາຍໄດ້."

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"ທັງໝົດນີ້ແມ່ນໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຟຣີໃນການສະໝັກໃຊ້ປະຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານ; ເຊີນທົດລອງໃຊ້ໄດ້ເລີຍ! 🙃"

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"They primarily use the Point of Sale application, along with Inventory, "
"Sales, and Purchase apps. For businesses looking to expand online, the "
"Website and E-commerce applications are ideal for showcasing products and "
"handling online orders."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ແລ້ວ ພວກເຂົາຈະໃຊ້ແອັບ Point of Sale ຮ່ວມກັບແອັບສິນຄ້າຄົງຄັງ, ການຂາຍ, ແລະ ການຈັດ"
"ຊື້. ສຳລັບທຸລະກິດທີ່ຕ້ອງການຂະຫຍາຍທາງອອນລາຍ, ແອັບເວັບໄຊ ແລະ E-commerce ແມ່ນເໝາະສົມທີ່ສຸດໃນການ"
"ສະແດງສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ຈັດການຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ອອນລາຍ."

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This setup is tailored for cake shop companies selling directly to "
"consumers. Cake shops are businesses that specialize in offering a variety "
"of cakes, pastries, and other confectionery items, catering to personalized "
"and special orders for occasions like birthdays, weddings, and celebrations."
msgstr ""
"ການຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ຖືກອອກແບບມາສະເພາະສຳລັບທຸລະກິດຮ້ານເຄັກທີ່ຂາຍໃຫ້ກັບຜູ້ບໍລິໂພກໂດຍກົງ. ຮ້ານເຄັກແມ່ນທຸລະກິດທີ່ມີຄ"
"ວາມຊ່ຽວຊານໃນການສະເໜີເຄັກທີ່ຫຼາກຫຼາຍ, ເຂົ້າໜົມປັງ, ແລະ ສິນຄ້າປະເພດເຂົ້າໜົມອື່ນໆ, ເພື່ອຕອບສະໜອງຄຳສັ່ງ"
"ຊື້ສ່ວນຕົວ ແລະ ໂອກາດພິເສດ ເຊັ່ນ: ວັນເກີດ, ງານແຕ່ງດອງ, ແລະ ການສະເຫຼີມສະຫຼອງຕ່າງໆ."

